This guy (Ron) canceled my reservation the same day he charged my card....
I sent these guys an email a week or two ago asking about availability for August. We emailed back and forth a bit then I just called because I thought that would be easier. I called him as soon as I received the email. He told me he was tied up and to call him back later because he would inevitably forget. Okay, a bit unprofessional but whatever.
I was unavailable so my partner contacted him. We wanted to ask some questions about adding a driver, some of the equipment that is supposed to be included and a few other things. He was apparently too busy to answer questions and told my partner to Contact him in the morning.
Then he sent me an email later that day saying if I didn't give him the credit card information he was going to cancel my reservation request.
I responded as soon as I saw it saying, why would you do that? I've tried to give you my credit card twice and you weren't available to help me.!
I called him right away and he told me that my partner never offered to give the credit information, which is not true. I thought that was really odd but told him we still wanted to confirm our reservation if it was still available and chalked it up to a misunderstanding.
